octetos-biblion
------------------------------------------
Library for reading biblia

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libbiblion0-0.1.1alpha-1bl2
  libconfig++-devel-1.8.2-1bl1
  libconfig++15-1.8.2-1bl1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  liboctetos-core-devel-2.62.1beta-1bl1
  liboctetos-core0-2.62.1beta-1bl1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  CUnit-2.1.3-1
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  bison-3.8.2-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libconfig++-devel-1.8.2-1bl1
  liboctetos-core-devel-2.62.1beta-1bl1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/azaeldevel/octetos-biblion

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/azaeldevel/octetos-biblion/archive/refs/tags/0.1.1-alpha.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack octetos-biblion-0.1.1alpha-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./octetos-biblion-0.1.1alpha-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/octetos-biblion-0.1.1alpha-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/octetos-biblion-0.1.1alpha-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbiblion0-0.1.1alpha-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbiblion-devel-0.1.1alpha-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(octetos-biblion)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/octetos-biblion.README
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-biblion/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-biblion/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-biblion/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-biblion/INSTALL
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-biblion/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/octetos-biblion/README

(libbiblion0)
  /usr/bin/cygbiblion-0.dll

(libbiblion-devel)
  /usr/include/octetos/biblion/biblion.hh
  /usr/include/octetos/biblion/cita-lexer.h
  /usr/lib/libbiblion.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/octetos-biblion.pc

